data.title: Resources for Termination of service
data.meta_description: This ePublication presents the development of the main international organisations involved in European integration that have been set up in Western Europe since the end of the Second World War: the European Communities in the European Union (EU), the Council of Europe, Western European Union (WEU) and the Organisation for Security and Cooperation in Europe (OSCE).
